I think we need one last category.  Most potential.  Examples of 
chars with great potential would be Eyebright, since we haven't seen 
what he'll be like full grown, Shadow Star, as he makes his army of 
slaves, and Legacy, because he could change history by following in 
Megatrons footsteps and destroying the Protohumans along with all 
other organic life on Earth.
